profile: Shuswap Tree Service is a family owned and operated business. Our mission is to provide the Shuswap and North Okanagan  region  with comprehensive tree removal and arborist services.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Our primary business is the removal of dangerous, difficult and storm damaged trees.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        We can deal with steep slopes, tight locations, close buildings, power lines or any other obstacles that may be encountered in  safe, effective and timely manner.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          In some cases it may be necessary to use low impact  take down. This is done by lowering small tree sections to the ground  and carrying away, Or by aerial rigging away from the tree and directly to the chipping area, thus avoiding drag damage to a  lawn or landscaping.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              We honour our estimates and will stand by them unless the scale or scope of the job changes                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Shuswap Tree Service is licensed and insured                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Give us a call to dicuss your tree management needs
